WHEREAS, while Melissa is retiring from the profession, she certainly has no plans
to slow down, and is looking forward to celebrating her parents' upcoming seventy-fifth
wedding anniversary, traveling with family, and spending time with her four young
grandchildren.
THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED that the Senate of the Legislature of Louisiana
does hereby commend and congratulate Melissa Adams on the occasion of her retirement
from Ochsner Medical Center - West Bank and to recognize her many accomplishments
throughout her career.
BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that a copy of this Resolution be transmitted to
Melissa Adams.
PRESIDENT OF THE SENATE
